<br>
So:<br>
Name: Hire<br>
Cost: 10 RA points<br>
Duration: 30 sec every 30 min, insta cast.<br>
Does: You hire ( ingame it would be like a summon) a lvl 50 cleric with 40 Rejuvenation, chain casting the lvl 30 spreadheal ( he can't be interuped, but can be mezzed/stunned).<br>
<br>
<br>
I don't think this RA is overpowered or underpowered, but it gives us something to help the group. And gives something extra why you would take a merc in your group (like bof, fh,sos,..).<br>
<br>
I don't belive in damage RA's, did you know that the sorc RA AE DOT does around 1000 damage ( can kill a non-sc caster alown), but yet have to see it helped a group ( I only use it to farm in a seige/zerg).<br>
<br>
RA's that give us a ton damage/reduse AF, will make merc hit too hard, and ask zerkers about what will happens then.. <p>Wou Mindbarrier  sorcere RR 6L5<br>
